0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\05\00\00\01\c6Emitted when a wallet's tracked net-deployed amount diverges from its\0aon-chain token balance at removal time. Informational only \e2\80\94 the vault\0adoes NOT use the tracker or the observed balance to adjust\0a`deployed_assets` on removal (that write-down is the admin's explicit\0aresponsibility via `update_deployed_assets`). Indicates either external\0adust sent to the wallet (tracked < balance) or an off-chain spend the\0avault did not drive (tracked > balance).\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\15WalletBalanceDiverged\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\17wallet_balance_diverged\00\00\00\00\03\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0asubaccount\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\14tracked_net_deployed\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0ewallet_balance\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\05\00\00\01\c1Emitted when the operator reconciles a wallet's attributed value via\0a`update_wallet_deployed` \e2\80\94 atomically moves both the per-wallet tracker\0aand the aggregate `deployed_assets` counter. `delta` is the signed\0achange applied to each (positive for recognised gains / dust recovery,\0anegative for losses). Distinct from `DeployedAssetsChanged`, which\0asignals an aggregate-only reconciliation (e.g. off-chain strategy AUM\0anot tied to a specific wallet).\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\15WalletDeployedUpdated\00\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\17wallet_deployed_updated\00\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\08operator\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0asubaccount\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0bold_tracked\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0bnew_tracked\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\05delta\00\00\00\00\00\00\0b\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\16AdminTransferCancelled\00\00\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\18admin_transfer_cancelled\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\05admin\00\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\01\00\00\00\02